{"tid":609274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國婚紗舖講明全人手製作，卻被踢爆原來全部都用中國貨！","createTime":"2018-03-29T01:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T08:18:24.000Z","uid":1886,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"66afe614970cc2224cc0888d5999624b7ee58ef0","tid":609274,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T01:54:13.000Z","msg":"英國一對母女在南威爾斯的紐波特商業街合力經營婚紗店，以人手製作、獨家訂製作招徠，每套婚紗索價700鎊(約7800港元)至1000鎊(約1.1萬港元)；然而，準新娘取得「獨一無二」的婚紗時，卻發現有「中國製造」的標籤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一眾顧客驚覺受騙，隨即在Facebook發起運動聲討<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1309121/org/6b8a806a53204c7343d55aa883c00df3.jpg/KiQ025NAtV5hu-vg-VphKFrgnqUKI7ut6AFMregBTK0?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1309121%2Forg%2F6b8a806a53204c7343d55aa883c00df3.jpg%2FKiQ025NAtV5hu-vg-VphKFrgnqUKI7ut6AFMregBTK0%3Fv%3Dw640&h=a68f2510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，36歲的婚紗店東畢曉普（Melanie Bishop）與60歲的母親在被「踢爆」不久就把婚紗店關門大吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，逾百名準新娘投訴無門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，擔心大喜之日無婚紗可穿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，於是向監察部門求助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1308859/org/aaa5e9f8f11e0f61db23369ef91ee966.jpg/K-zXdnAVcBkWF5G1SW5gGQ0KaVUYiHWLoN5M06DeTNM?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1308859%2Forg%2Faaa5e9f8f11e0f61db23369ef91ee966.jpg%2FK-zXdnAVcBkWF5G1SW5gGQ0KaVUYiHWLoN5M06DeTNM%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=46b03dfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名34歲的準新娘稱，這實在是可怕經歷，不單影響到家庭生活，還影響到工作。有55歲的準外母謂：「你總會預期女兒的婚禮一切都是完美的，我從沒有預期會變成這樣子的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/172117/獨一無二-婚紗貼-中國製造-標籤-準新娘聲討-店主關門\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F172117%2F%E7%8D%A8%E4%B8%80%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%8C-%E5%A9%9A%E7%B4%97%E8%B2%BC-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0-%E6%A8%99%E7%B1%A4-%E6%BA%96%E6%96%B0%E5%A8%98%E8%81%B2%E8%A8%8E-%E5%BA%97%E4%B8%BB%E9%97%9C%E9%96%80&d=P8inWNAKoWd%2BqwGhYM4UsgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=589aeea0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/172117/獨一無二-婚紗貼-中國製造-標籤-準新娘聲討-店主關門</a>"},{"pid":"def37e2e5f5539065efe5795b749552361a27b61","tid":609274,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T01:55:39.000Z","msg":"婚紗店東畢曉普（Melanie Bishop）與其老母<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1308861/org/2c4034b2bce9bd0e1eff89d612d623e1.jpg/iOeXi5tuYdlz6cboHhfXHRu9I6dUhAkIa_2es2v9nrM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1308861%2Forg%2F2c4034b2bce9bd0e1eff89d612d623e1.jpg%2FiOeXi5tuYdlz6cboHhfXHRu9I6dUhAkIa_2es2v9nrM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=df40cdff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n畢曉普卻認為，顧客應該知道只有中國製造的婚紗才會賣700鎊至1000鎊，並謂她才是這次「欺凌與謊言」的受害者，「在3個星期內，我名譽掃地，相信會失去房子、生計及一直努力經營的事業，當所有事情失控，我未曾停止過哭泣」。<br />\n<br />\n畢曉普強調，沒有刻意誤導顧客，婚紗確是自家設計，「那些女人認為我們的婚紗不值40鎊而且來自eBay，這實在太離譜，我們擁有一家有15名裁縫的工廠」。她表示，事件中自己唯一可以有不同做法的是，明確告訴顧客衣服的來源地，「但很多商店都是把物料及勞動力外判到中國」。<br />\n<br />\n結果，畢曉普與母親被檢察官根據2008年的《消費者免受不公平交易條例》告上法庭，兩人承認未有告知顧客婚紗其實是在中國製造，虛假聲稱是在當地的工作坊製作；法庭判兩人分別監禁6個月，緩刑1年零3個月。法官判刑時表示，某些婚紗不合身、顏色偏差及並非人手製作，但很多準新娘都已別無選擇，只好接受低質婚紗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"d7d6bf56990933433bd3aae76aac1b0df4f138aa","tid":609274,"uid":150523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T02:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n畢曉普卻認為，顧客應該知道只有中國製造的婚紗才會賣700鎊至1000鎊<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n條女係咪馬雲扮？同馬雲話淘寶冇假貨一樣"},{"pid":"b7a6725a66495dc7131d6d7c4295b9e9d5102785","tid":609274,"uid":66686,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T02:07:46.000Z","msg":"在中國人手製造？"},{"pid":"dcbd86ed290969a0aa0636f9ee519abe9d4d6fce","tid":609274,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b7a6725a66495dc7131d6d7c4295b9e9d5102785","tid":609274,"uid":66686,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T02:07:46.000Z","msg":"在中國人手製造？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T02:40:53.000Z","msg":"捉字蝨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7616b6f668e5531c343152e40a3185a57fbdfb5","tid":609274,"uid":160147,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T03:09:08.000Z","msg":"中國人唔係人手呀？？？"},{"pid":"d332807f60cb6cd5d133a13bb9b625cf58fdc067","tid":609274,"uid":9284,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T03:14:36.000Z","msg":"衰on9 牌都唔識剪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85a7ea7c1a36f1dee8616471f5b2c7adf0ad08e","tid":609274,"uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T03:15:22.000Z","msg":"獨一無二、人手製造同中國製造無衝突喎"},{"pid":"821c87520b4bfda15fc84afa51021e8366b12d9f","tid":609274,"uid":167574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e7616b6f668e5531c343152e40a3185a57fbdfb5","tid":609274,"uid":160147,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T03:09:08.000Z","msg":"中國人唔係人手呀？？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T03:15:58.000Z","msg":"蟲手製造"},{"pid":"e7d4cbbfbd7299ed094d4d66a6829252146ac88e","tid":609274,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T03:16:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e47baac25f40105139728563fee3e19a874111f","tid":609274,"uid":4285,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,